                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240603-15-victim201 t18240603-15-viclabel81"></join>. On the 9th of May, between nine and ten o'clock in the evening, I was in <placeName id="t18240603-15-crimeloc82">Newgate-street, near the Old Bailey</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18240603-15-crimeloc82" type="placeName" value="Newgate-street, near the Old Bailey"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18240603-15-crimeloc82" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240603-15-off79 t18240603-15-crimeloc82"></join>, with a friend, and felt something taken from my pocket; I turned round to the prisoner, who was passing between me and Newgate, and seeing me turn round so quick he put my handkerchief down on the ground, and ran off - I saw him do it; I took it up, and ran after him - I overtook him without losing sight of him.</p>
